    ONLINE_IMAGE_SERVER                 'ONLINE|200|OnlineImageServer|–°–Ķ—Ä–≤–Ķ—Ä –ł–∑–ĺ–Ī—Ä–į–∂–Ķ–Ĺ–ł–Ļ',
    ONLINE_ENABLE                       'ONLINE|201|OnlineEnable|–í–ļ–Ľ—é—á–ł—ā—Ć On-line —Ä–Ķ–∂–ł–ľ|1',
